title: Sanford and Son 1972-1977 (Complete TV series in MP4 format)
description:
Sanford and Son TV series - Complete Series from 1972 to 1977 in MP4 format. 


While the role of Fred G. Sanford was known for his bigotry and cantankerousness, the role of Lamont Sanford was that of Fred's long suffering conscientious peacemaker. At times, both characters would involve themselves in schemes, usually as a means of earning cash quickly in order to pay off their various debts. Other colorful and unconventional characters on the show included Aunt Esther, Grady Wilson, Bubba Bexley and Rollo Lawson
